  {
    "page_no": 10,
    "block_id": "p10_b14",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "聲譽，體現友邦保險誠可信賴、強韌穩健，並堅持為持分者做對的事。自2020年初以來，2019冠狀病毒病大流",
    "translation": "reputation reflecting our trustworthiness, resilience and commitment to doing right by our stakeholders. Since early 2020, the COVID-19 pandemic has created an increasingly complex business environment with unprecedented shifts in political, macroeconomic and capital market conditions. In such an environment,",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
