  {
    "page_no": 10,
    "block_id": "p10_b15",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "行導致營商環境不斷變化及日趨複雜，而政治、宏觀經濟及資本市場亦出現前所未見的轉移。在這樣的環境下，",
    "translation": "AIA's financial strength and our purpose of helping people live healthier, longer, better lives have become even more significant. I am deeply grateful to all AIA employees, agents and partners who, despite facing severe challenges, have cared for the community, fulfilled their duties and remained focused on supporting our customers,",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
