  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b21",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "儘管2020年的新業務價值27.65億美元較2019年減少了33%，我們迅速採用了新的數碼工具，並且外出限制的普",
    "translation": "Although new business value of USD 2.765 billion in 2020 decreased 33% versus 2019, we rapidly adopted new digital tools, and relaxation of movement restrictions supported sales recovery.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.49,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.595,
    "font_size_final": 5.36,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b22",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "遍放寬支持了銷售勢頭的恢復。友邦保險中國業務為2020年本集團的新業務價值帶來最大貢獻，也是我們第一個",
    "translation": "AIA's China business made the largest contribution to Group new business value in 2020 and was the first reporting segment to show sales recovery, as the region gradually relaxed strict lockdowns from March 2020 onwards.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.463,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.507,
    "font_size_final": 4.56,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b23",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "顯示銷售勢頭有所恢復的報告分部，原因在於該地區自2020年3月逐步放寬嚴格的封鎖。撇除維持低位的中國內",
    "translation": "Excluding new business sales from Mainland China visitors to Hong Kong, which remained low, the Group's other segments showed strong recovery in new business value in the second half, growing 23% versus the first half.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.477,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.508,
    "font_size_final": 4.58,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b24",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "地訪港旅客銷售額，本集團其他分部的新業務價值在下半年強勁復甦，與上半年相比增長了23%。本集團的新業",
    "translation": "The Group's new business momentum remained strong in 2021, with new business value in the first two months 15% higher than the corresponding 2020 period.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.644,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.68,
    "font_size_final": 6.12,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b25",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "務發展勢頭在2021年持續強勁，首兩個月新業務價值較2020年同期高出15%。",
    "translation": "AIA's China business recorded successful momentum in 2021, with new business value in the first two months showing very strong growth versus the corresponding 2020 period.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.444,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.444,
    "font_size_final": 4.0,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b26",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "友邦保險中國業務在2021年錄得成功的勢頭，首兩個月的新業務價值與2020年同期比較，錄得非常強勁的增",
    "translation": "New business value of USD 968 million in 2020 decreased 17% versus 2019, primarily due to limited sales in the first quarter following the initial COVID-19 outbreak.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.646,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.691,
    "font_size_final": 6.22,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b27",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "長。2020年新業務價值9.68億美元較2019年減少17%，主要由於2019冠狀病毒病在第一季爆發初期而導致銷售額",
    "translation": "As movement restrictions eased, new business momentum improved rapidly. New business value resumed customary seasonal patterns, with greater concentration in the first half.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.567,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.636,
    "font_size_final": 5.72,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b28",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "有限。隨著外出限制放寬，新業務動力得以迅速改善。新業務價值重拾我們慣常的季節性規律，比重更側重於上",
    "translation": "In 2020, AIA's China business made the largest contribution to the Group's new business value.",
    "translation_source": "model_initial",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": false,
    "fit_status_initial": "ok",
    "fit_status_final": "ok",
    "font_ratio_initial": 1.0,
    "font_ratio_final": 1.0,
    "font_size_final": 9.0,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b29",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "半年。在2020年，友邦保險中國業務為集團的新業務價值帶來最大貢獻。",
    "translation": "Following implementation of travel restrictions, new business sales from Mainland China visitors to AIA's Hong Kong business were virtually suspended from early February 2020, resulting in significant decline in new business value.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.444,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.444,
    "font_size_final": 4.0,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b30",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "在實施旅遊限制後，友邦保險香港業務來自中國內地訪港客戶的新業務銷售自2020年2月初起實際上已暫停，導",
    "translation": "The new business value margin declined, reflecting underwriting expense overruns due to reduced new business volume, product mix changes and lower interest rate effects.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.553,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.628,
    "font_size_final": 5.65,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b31",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "致其新業務價值大幅下降。新業務價值利潤率錄得跌幅，反映新業務量減少導致承保開支超支、產品組合變動及",
    "translation": "Macau resumed the individual travel scheme for Mainland China visitors at end-September 2020. This supported recovery of new business sales from Mainland China visitors to Macau, which accounted for more than one-third of AIA Macau's total annualized new premiums in Q4.",
    "translation_source": "model_compact",
    "control_rule": "",
    "used_compact_retry": true,
    "fit_status_initial": "font_shrink",
    "fit_status_final": "font_shrink",
    "font_ratio_initial": 0.444,
    "font_ratio_final": 0.444,
    "font_size_final": 4.0,
    "layout_mode_initial": "single_line",
    "layout_mode_final": "single_line"
  },
  {
    "page_no": 20,
    "block_id": "p20_b32",
    "block_type": "body",
    "source_text": "利率下降的影響所致。澳門在2020年9月底恢復中國內地旅客個人遊計劃。這為澳門的中國內地訪澳客戶銷售回",
